data.description: Come check out this unique style 3-bedroom, 3-bath semi-attached home in Bay Terrace, Staten Island! One of the only homes currently listed in Bay Terrace. This home has amazing potential for the perfect buyer. As soon as you step inside, you'll see the cozy layout, which makes it feel like a warm place to call home. The kitchen is nicely appointed with shiny stainless steel appliances, and perfect place for a grand meal or simply enjoy a nice breakfast with your family. The living room area creates great vibes and is just the right spot to unwind after a long day. Upstairs, you'll find three roomy bedrooms, so there's plenty of space for you and your family or maybe a guest room for friends who pop in. The primary bedroom fits a king size bed. When the weather's nice, head outside to the backyard for some relaxation under the sun. The location is a real bonus-Bay Terrace is a lovely neighborhood with parks, schools, and cool hangouts nearby. So, if you're looking for a modest and charming home that's just waiting for the perfect owner, this might be the one for you. Don't wait too long to check it out!
